Paper: hep-th/9807226

Date: 1998-07-30

Title: Geometric Holography, the Renormalization Group and the c-Theorem

Authors: Enrique Alvarez and Cesar Gomez

Comments: 28 pages, Latex, 2 figures

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B541 (1999) 441-460

In this paper the whole geometrical set-up giving a conformally invariantholographic projection of a diffeomorphism invariant bulk theory is clarified.By studying the renormalization group flow along null geodesic congruences aholographic version of Zamolodchikov's c-theorem is proven.